Tsukasanosuke: “Everyone! Please help us! Let us all sing together!”
Skiers: Haha! That sounds fun! Let's do it!
Skiers: Yeah!
An: Everyone on the slopes! I hope you're all ready! And try to keep up, okay?!
An & Kohane: ♪————————!
Skiers: Whoa...! I have no idea what's going on, but something amazing's just begun!
Skiers: This is so cool!
Akito: Geez, they're gonna melt all the snow if they're not careful...
Tsukasa: (They got the crowd this excited in so little time...!)
Tsukasa: (Their energy! Their ability to invigorate an audience! This is incredible!)
Tsukasa: (I would definitely love to have this sort of explosiveness!)
Tsukasa: Nicely done, Shiraishi! You had the entire ski resort eating out of your hand!
An: Haha! Thank you very much! I had a lot of fun being a part of your show!
Kohane: An, you were so cool just now...!
Akito: Yeah, you sure do tend to leap before looking.
An: Hey, what's that supposed to mean?
Nene: Tsukasa! We're all set to move to our next location!
Tsukasa: Wonderful! Parting is such sweet sorrow, but we must get going!
Tsukasa: Thank you all for participating! Until next time! Farewell!
